N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4815.5 - List of employees, agents or representatives

State Regulations

The application shall be accompanied by a statement on
form BC-108 as prescribed by the commission, containing a list of all
employees, agents or representatives of the applicant. Notes
